title: Can't see any emails after upgraded to 115.
content: My Thunderbird was upgraded to 115 automatically, and now I can't see any emails (old and new). Just a blank page. I don't have a backup. How can I resolve this issue? Tried the troubleshooting mode, but didn't help. I've been using TB since 2006, and have thousands of emails in my profile, so can't just create a new profile.
